{
  "stem": "20142.9",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there-- there were these friends of mine who, when I returned from the latrine, pulled me down and said, stop creating any more problem than we already have.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are waiting peacefully for something to happen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said there is nobody at the watchtower.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't believe me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And finally, one of the people had to go to execute his daily duties and he notices too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he conducted himself the same way as I did, by throwing a pebble at the watchtower.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And evidently, he hit the machine gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the sound of this was like clinking [BACKROUND NOISE] in the air.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is Alpine mountain, very cool mornings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he ran into barracks and he said, there is nobody on the watchtower.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There is no, there are no Germans around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then-- then people start getting out of the barracks and really trying to see if this is true, that the Germans had left as it was standing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And sure enough, we got out from the-- Mathausen was having several small camps in one, in this huge camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we got out from our barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We got to the main appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And what we witnessed was a American tank prying the gate of the-- huge gate there was, all usually open by two-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two group of people, for closing and opening, that was their duty, of the gate, was made out of locks.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was a very heavy and very well built.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, the American tank was prying it and succeeded to break through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then when I have seen the Americans walking, pouring in in the camp with the guns and looking at us, people were getting out, out of the way.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
